thread.title: BRIEF-Jana Partners Cuts Sole Share Stake In Conagra Brands, Zayo Group

title: BRIEF-Jana Partners Cuts Sole Share Stake In Conagra Brands, Zayo Group

organizations.name: brief-jana partners cuts sole share stake in conagra brands

text:
Feb 14 (Reuters) - JANA PARTNERS LLC:
* JANA PARTNERS LLC CUTS SOLE SHARE STAKE IN CONAGRA BRANDS INC BY 35 PERCENT TO 3.2 MILLION SHARES - SEC FILING
* JANA PARTNERS LLC CUTS SOLE SHARE STAKE IN ZAYO GROUP HOLDINGS INC BY 46 PERCENT TO 2.3 MILLION SHARES
* JANA PARTNERS LLC DISSOLVES SOLE SHARE STAKE IN SALESFORCE.COM
* JANA PARTNERS LLC - CHANGE IN HOLDINGS ARE AS OF DEC 31, 2017 AND COMPARED WITH THE PREVIOUS QUARTER ENDED AS OF SEPT 30, 2017 Source text for quarter ended Dec 31, 2017: ( bit.ly/2Er4MQh ) Source text for quarter ended Sept 30, 2017 ( bit.ly/2igoLbb )
